2630:../../Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_tim.c ****   *         channels 1 and channel 2 are reserved and cannot be used for other
2631:../../Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_tim.c ****   *         purpose.
